"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Sleep cycles typically last around 90 minutes to 2 hours, during which time the brain cycles from slow-wave sleep to REM sleep.  Sleep cycles are succession of NREM-REMs periods.  </p>\n"
